title: Inelastic scattering of neutrons with initial energy 9.1+-0.2 MeV and the density of nuclear levels .

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.19, p.608 (1974)
Jour: Yadernaya Fizika, Vol.19, Issue.6, p.1190 (1974)

x4freetext: Inelastic scattering of neutrons with initial energy
9.1+-0.2 MeV  and the density of nuclear levels .
.Hollow cylinders with outer diameter 5 cm, inner
diameter 1.5 cm, length 6 cm. Natural isotope mixture.
Time of flight method with resolution 2.5 nsec/m,
For monitoring: two counters - all-wave and
Cross sections were measured relative to the (n,p)
scattering cross section taken from fast
I.B.Marion and I.L.Fowler, New York, London, 1960.
.Corrections is introduced on multiple scattering and
receiving of nuclear temperature and nuclear level
SD: Updated to new date formats,lower case.
Ref. on Engl.transl. of YF added. ERR-T -> DATA-ERR.
M.M. Article was checked, BIB information
EN was corrected 9.2 -> 9.1 ( as given in articles)

and error of determination of energy corresponding
Data are presented on Fig.4 of SNP,19,608,1974
